A six-year-old KwaZulu-Natal girl, who was reported kidnapped near Glendale on Sunday, has been found dead. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - A six-year-old KwaZulu-Natal girl, who was reported kidnapped near Glendale on Sunday, has been found dead. After an extensive search, rescuers found her body in the Glendale area on the North Coast on Tuesday afternoon. READ: Tongaat teen murder accused back in court Police are investigating her disappearance and cause of death.